<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Store Created Successfully - Admin Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link href="/css/admin.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            --success-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #56ab2f 0%, #a8e6cf 100%);
            --card-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            --success-color: #198754;
        }

        .success-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }

        .success-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            padding: 3rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .success-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 6px;
            background: var(--success-gradient);
        }

        .success-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: var(--success-color);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            40% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
            60% {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
            }
        }

        .success-title {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .success-subtitle {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .store-info-panel {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(25, 135, 84, 0.05) 0%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.05) 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(25, 135, 84, 0.2);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .store-info-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(25, 135, 84, 0.2);
        }

        .store-info-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--success-color);
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }

        .store-info-title {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .store-info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .store-info-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .store-info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .store-info-value {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .store-url {
            color: var(--success-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .store-url:hover {
            color: var(--success-color);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .action-card {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .action-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .action-card:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .action-card:hover {
            border-color: #667eea;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 1rem 2rem rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        .action-card.primary {
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            color: white;
            border-color: #667eea;
        }

        .action-card.primary:hover {
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 1rem 2rem rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        .action-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: block;
        }

        .action-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .action-description {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .next-steps {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .next-steps-title {
            color: #495057;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .next-steps-icon {
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .next-steps-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .next-steps-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
        }

        .next-steps-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .next-steps-item i {
            color: var(--success-color);
            margin-right: 1rem;
            margin-top: 0.2rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .badge-template {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .success-card {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
                margin: 1rem;
                border-radius: 1rem;
            }

            .success-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .success-subtitle {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .store-info-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .action-buttons {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .action-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            .action-icon {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .action-title {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-container">
        <div class="success-card">
            <div class="success-icon">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="success-title">ðŸŽ‰ Store Created Successfully!</h1>
            <p class="success-subtitle">
                Congratulations! Your store "<%= store.name %>" has been created and deployed successfully. 
                <br>Your store is now live and ready for customization.
            </p>

            <div class="store-info-panel">
                <div class="store-info-header">
                    <i class="bi bi-shop store-info-icon"></i>
                    <h3 class="store-info-title"><%= store.name %></h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="store-info-grid">
                    <div class="store-info-item">
                        <span class="store-info-label">Store URL</span>
                        <a href="<%= store.deployment_url.startsWith('http') ? store.deployment_url : 'https://' + store.deployment_url %>" target="_blank" class="store-url">
                            <%= store.deployment_url.startsWith('http') ? store.deployment_url : 'https://' + store.deployment_url %>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="store-info-item">
                        <span class="store-info-label">Template</span>
                        <span class="store-info-value">
                            <span class="badge-template">
                                <i class="bi bi-palette me-1"></i>
                                <%= store.template ? (store.template.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + store.template.slice(1).replace('-', ' ')) : 'Bootstrap Default' %>
                            </span>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="store-info-item">
                        <span class="store-info-label">Country & Language</span>
                        <span class="store-info-value">
                            <i class="bi bi-globe me-2"></i>
                            <%= store.country.toUpperCase() %> - <%= store.language.toUpperCase() %>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="store-info-item">
                        <span class="store-info-label">Status</span>
                        <span class="store-info-value">
                            <span class="badge bg-success">
                                <i class="bi bi-check-circle me-1"></i>
                                Live & Ready
                            </span>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="/admin/store/<%= store.uuid %>/content" class="action-card primary">
                    <i class="bi bi-pencil-square action-icon"></i>
                    <h4 class="action-title">Edit Content</h4>
                    <p class="action-description">
                        Customize your store's content, images, and text to match your brand
                    </p>
                </a>
                
                <a href="/admin/store/<%= store.uuid %>/pages" class="action-card">
                    <i class="bi bi-files action-icon"></i>
                    <h4 class="action-title">Manage Pages</h4>
                    <p class="action-description">
                        Enable, disable, or reorganize your store pages and navigation
                    </p>
                </a>
                
                <a href="<%= store.deployment_url.startsWith('http') ? store.deployment_url : 'https://' + store.deployment_url %>" target="_blank" class="action-card">
                    <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right action-icon"></i>
                    <h4 class="action-title">View Live Store</h4>
                    <p class="action-description">
                        See your store as customers will see it and test the experience
                    </p>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h5 class="next-steps-title">
                    <i class="bi bi-lightbulb next-steps-icon"></i>
                    What's Next?
                </h5>
                <ul class="next-steps-list">
                    <li class="next-steps-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-check2"></i>
                        <span>All essential pages have been created with default content</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="next-steps-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-check2"></i>
                        <span>Your store is deployed and accessible at the URL above</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="next-steps-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        <span><strong>Recommended:</strong> Start by editing your homepage content to reflect your brand</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="next-steps-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        <span>Add your products and customize product pages</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="next-steps-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        <span>Review and customize legal pages (privacy policy, terms, etc.)</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>